node.text: with @kit.griffiths and @alannah.carr . After a great day on the boat with @graceshorevillas , we slowly made our way back and saw a couple dolphins breach. I masked up, grabbed my @gopro and hopped in. This first clip is the moment I was underwater looking for the dolphins and they appeared in the distance. They swam right by, looked right at me, and turned around to come play. From that moment we played with them for about 20 minutes until the mom decided it was time to go and moved Dreamer along with her tail fin against its dorsal fin keeping her moving along not to get distracted by playing again.  Here’s a condensed version of our 20 minute interaction with these amazing creatures. I was blown away by the interaction and communication. I grew up around dolphins in coastal GA but never seen wild dolphins interact with humans in this way. There was clearly mutual communication and interaction going on here, and truly made me realize how these animals are the closest living things to humans in the ocean. #dolphin #dolphins #marinelife #turksandcaicos #tci #ocean #nature #wildlife #islandvibes #paradise

node.text: Absolutely hyped to be one of the first to get my hands on the all new @gopro Hero10 Black. Every year I wonder how these things can get any better and somehow they do it. In a nutshell- new CP2 chip, higher frame speeds, and even better stabilization. Shoutout to @_connerjohn for putting the full edit on the YouTube together so quickly and @solaglocal for capturing the water shots. #gopro #goprohero10 #hero10black

node.text: It was ultra satisfying to slide out to this backside while the wave was already standing tall and breaking a lot closer. I actually slipped on the drop, but still had plenty of speed to make it to the wave and drive down the line. I love this video because it really shows just how amazing this place is for skimboarding. Shoutout to @chase.jagger , @raimanaworld , @wsl , @kswaveco , for allowing me the opportunity to skim it. @kellyslater #skimboarding #surfing #surfranch #wsl #skimboard

node.text: Absolutely stoked to be able to skim into the best skimboarding wave in the world again- @kswaveco . Huge shoutout to @chase.jagger , @wsl , and the entire @kswaveco crew for taking the necessary precautions to allow me the opportunity. I really never thought I’d be able to do it again. I hope one day we can have a skim event here. A skimboard really is the board of choice for this awesome man made wave 👌- I was playing it pretty safe on this wave, but I could only imagine what could be done on a skimboard here with more opportunities. Here’s the phone clip by @agency133 📷 while the legend @raimanaworld does his thing on the jet ski “STAY LOW!” 😂🤙. @kellyslater 🐐 #skimboarding #surfranch #surfing #kswaveco #wsl #actionsports

node.text: Nothing like sharing pure stoke for your friends as they get barreled out of their mind. @patstacyfilm capturing a high level stoke moment at the @kswaveco as I watch my friend @chase.jagger getting absolutely shacked! What a day! #surfranch #surfing

node.text: On the next episode of @ultimatesurferabc …skimboarder breaks into the surf ranch and lands the highest scoring wave of the day 😂🤘. Throwback to my first wave ever at the Surf Ranch captured by @blake_ernst 📷- and possibly the only wave that will ever be skimmed out to… Full Story in my BIO link. #ultimatesurfer #theultimatesurfer #surfing #surfranch #skimboarding
